  "description": "<b>宏日前确认说，公司将于&#160;2014&#160;年发布自家的可穿戴式电子产品。</b>宏智能手机事业部总裁刘思泰（ST&#160;Liew）在一次采访中说：“我们正在关注可穿戴式设备领域，我认为每一家消费者产品公司都应该关注可穿戴式设备……这项产业现在还有进入爆发期，但它具有数十亿美元的价值。”这样的说法或许能够体现出宏对此抱有的信心。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d4f698e/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241176.htm&amp;t=%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E5%AE%8F%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E8%BF%9B%E5%86%9B%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241176.htm&amp;t=%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E5%AE%8F%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E8%BF%9B%E5%86%9B%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241176.htm&amp;t=%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E5%AE%8F%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E8%BF%9B%E5%86%9B%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241176.htm&amp;t=%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E5%AE%8F%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%A4%E8%BF%9B%E5%86%9B%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241176.htm&amp;t=%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83+%E5%A